import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import './navigation-links.css' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route } from 'react-router-dom' const NavigationLinks = (props) => { return (
window.location.reload()} className="navbar-link" > {props.text} {props.text1} {props.text2} {props.text3} {props.text4}
) } NavigationLinks.defaultProps = { text2: 'Features', text3: 'Blog', rootClassName: '', text4: 'Pricing', text: 'Home', text1: 'About', } NavigationLinks.propTypes = { text2: PropTypes.string, text3: PropTypes.string, rootClassName: PropTypes.string, text4: PropTypes.string, text: PropTypes.string, text1: PropTypes.string, } export default NavigationLinks
